todomato

Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • todomato.Command

  • public class Command
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores the different components of a user's command: the action, and the argument. The action is the keyword specified in the first word of a command (eg. add, delete, update, etc), and the argument is the rest of the command.
